{"pageProps":{"entry":{"id":"local-hometown-to-silicon-valley-threshold","title":"From Night Markets to a One-Way Flight","date":"2016-06-01","slug":"hometown-to-silicon-valley-threshold","categories":["Life","Learning"],"mood":"Reflective","summary":"Before Silicon Valley, there was a kid shaped by night markets, failure, and a quiet decision to try one more time.","wordCount":538,"location":"Taiwan","source":"local","mdxSources":{"en":{"compiledSource":"var m=Object.defineProperty,u=Object.defineProperties;var d=Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptors;var a=Object.getOwnPropertySymbols;var s=Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty,p=Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable;var r=(e,t,n)=>t in e?m(e,t,{enumerable:!0,configurable:!0,writable:!0,value:n}):e[t]=n,o=(e,t)=>{for(var n in t||(t={}))s.call(t,n)&&r(e,n,t[n]);if(a)for(var n of a(t))p.call(t,n)&&r(e,n,t[n]);return e},h=(e,t)=>u(e,d(t));var l=(e,t)=>{var n={};for(var i in e)s.call(e,i)&&t.indexOf(i)<0&&(n[i]=e[i]);if(e!=null&&a)for(var i of a(e))t.indexOf(i)<0&&p.call(e,i)&&(n[i]=e[i]);return n};const layoutProps={},MDXLayout=\"wrapper\";function MDXContent(n){var i=n,{components:e}=i,t=l(i,[\"components\"]);return mdx(MDXLayout,h(o(o({},layoutProps),t),{components:e,mdxType:\"MDXLayout\"}),mdx(\"h1\",null,\"From Night Markets to a One-Way Flight\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"There\\u2019s a specific smell to a Taiwanese night market at 11pm \\u2014 scallion pancakes on a flat iron griddle, stinky tofu from three stalls down, and sugar cane juice sweating in a plastic cup.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"That was my childhood.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Not ambition. Not strategy. Just instinct: follow what feels right, one step at a time.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`I didn\\u2019t grow up thinking about Silicon Valley.\nI grew up thinking about where to eat next.`),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"The First Shift\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"University was the first time life stopped being automatic.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I chose computer science without a master plan. It wasn\\u2019t passion in the romantic sense \\u2014 it was curiosity. Code felt honest. You either solved the problem, or you didn\\u2019t. No politics, no guessing.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"But something changed quietly.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Late nights stopped being about exams and started being about possibilities. I found myself reading essays about startups and builders \\u2014 people who weren\\u2019t just solving problems, but deciding \",mdx(\"em\",{parentName:\"p\"},\"which problems mattered\"),\".\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`For the first time, I realized:\nThere\\u2019s a bigger game being played somewhere else.`),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"The Decision That Didn\\u2019t Feel Big\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I didn\\u2019t make a bold, cinematic decision.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"There was no \\u201CI\\u2019m going to change my life\\u201D moment.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"It was smaller than that.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,mdx(\"em\",{parentName:\"p\"},\"I\\u2019ll just apply once.\")),mdx(\"p\",null,\"That was it.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"One internship. One attempt. Just to see if I could even get close.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"Failure, Repeated Clearly\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"The process wasn\\u2019t designed for someone like me.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Different language. Different expectations. Different rules I didn\\u2019t grow up learning.\"),mdx(\"ul\",null,mdx(\"li\",{parentName:\"ul\"},\"Resume rewritten in English, again and again\"),mdx(\"li\",{parentName:\"ul\"},\"Interviews at 7am, trying to sound confident while half-awake\"),mdx(\"li\",{parentName:\"ul\"},\"Coding questions that felt more like performance than engineering\")),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I failed my first attempt.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Then the second.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Then the third.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Not \\u201Calmost.\\u201D Not \\u201Cclose.\\u201D Just \\u2014 no.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`At some point, it stops being about skill.\nIt becomes a question of identity:`),mdx(\"p\",null,mdx(\"em\",{parentName:\"p\"},\"Are you someone who keeps going, or someone who quietly adjusts their expectations?\")),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"The One That Went Through\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"The fourth time wasn\\u2019t dramatically different.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Same preparation. Same uncertainty. Same doubt in the background.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"But this time, something clicked.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"A callback. Then another round. Then silence that felt longer than it actually was.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"And then:\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"An offer.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"No celebration. No big reaction. Just a quiet moment of disbelief.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`Because deep down, I knew \\u2014\nThis wasn\\u2019t the result of confidence.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"It was the result of not stopping.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"The In-Between Space\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Six weeks later, I was holding a one-way ticket.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`Two suitcases.\nAn address I had never seen in person.\nA version of myself I hadn\\u2019t met yet.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Everything familiar stayed behind \\u2014 language, rhythm, the unspoken rules of how to exist comfortably.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"What I carried forward wasn\\u2019t certainty.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"It was something more fragile, but more important:\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"The willingness to step into a world where I didn\\u2019t belong \\u2014 yet.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"What This Chapter Means\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Looking back, this phase of my life wasn\\u2019t about success.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"It was about \",mdx(\"strong\",{parentName:\"p\"},\"permission\"),\".\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`Permission to try without guarantees.\nPermission to fail without redefining myself downward.\nPermission to choose a harder path without explaining it to everyone.`),mdx(\"p\",null,`Taiwan gave me instinct.\nFailure gave me clarity.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"And somewhere between the two, I earned the right to take that flight.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"The next chapter begins when the plane lands.\"))}MDXContent.isMDXComponent=!0;\n","scope":{}},"zh":{"compiledSource":"var i=Ob